@startuml simple_sequence_diagram

participant Pipeline
participant DriftDetector
participant DecisionEngine
participant ModelTrainer
participant PerformanceGate
participant ShadowEvaluator

Pipeline -> DriftDetector: Check drift
DriftDetector --> Pipeline: Drift detected

Pipeline -> DecisionEngine: Should retrain?
DecisionEngine --> Pipeline: Yes

Pipeline -> ModelTrainer: Train new model
ModelTrainer --> Pipeline: New model

Pipeline -> PerformanceGate: Evaluate
PerformanceGate --> Pipeline: Accept

Pipeline -> ShadowEvaluator: Start shadow test
ShadowEvaluator --> Pipeline: Promote after 20 cycles

@enduml
